\#\#\# Top Answer: Since you're working with a select element, perhaps you intended to use the [change event](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/change_event)? The [select event](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/select_event) is for selecting text in a text input.

